---
import InstructionNote from '../InstructionNote.astro';
---
<section id="voice">
    <h2>Voice & Language</h2>
    
    <InstructionNote>
        Define the reading level and communication style of your brand. Create a "Do / Don't" list for plain language, and set structural rules for formatting social media.
    </InstructionNote>

    <h3>Plain Language Guidelines</h3>
    <p>Splitli is written at a 6th-8th grade reading level to ensure accessibility and quick learning for everyone. The general tone of the website is clear, direct, and encouraging. The website’s aim is to provide information that makes fitness feel unintimidating and achievable. Our sentence structure guidelines keep sentences at a short to medium length to guarantee understanding. </p>

